name: Sinister
description:
Excuse me, I don't mean to be rude, But i'd rather not talk about my Monday mood. I had a bourbon for breakfast then ran into a metaphor head first! and i fear this is jus the prelude.

Now the whole world is spinning and my demons seem to be grinning dancing to the soundtrack of my misery "Why is this floor suddenly so slippery!" THUD!

I think they're winning.
